eDownload✅TwitterUpload using upload file functionalityDownload❌TwitterLink to imageClick on Link✅Doesn&#x27;t render properly unless hosting has og tagInstagramNew post (ensure original ratio/ not cropped etc.)No way to download, can expect src to get uploaded image❌LinkedInUpload in postNatively embedded✅LinkedInUpload in postDownload image❌DiscordUpload fileOpen hosted link❌Strips metadataDiscordUpload fileDownload file from hosted link❌GmailAttach file to emailClick preview❌GmailAttach file to emailDownload✅GmailEmbed file in emailDownload✅GmailEmbed file in emailClick preview❌\\nNote: Cloudflare Images also supports C2PA.\",\"title\":\"Image Metadata Stripping\",\"titles\":[]}]}}"
